<h5>This project is a simple blog created from Markdown files. It watches the files for changes, deletes and for newly created md files.</h5>

<h3>Tools:</h3>
<ul>
    <li>MD to HTML - <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/showdownjs/showdown">showdown</a> (alternative - <a target="_blank" href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/markdown-it">markdown-it</a>)</li>
    <li>cache - <a target="_blank" href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/node-cache">node-cache</a></li>
    <li>file watcher - <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/paulmillr/chokidar">chokidar</a></li>
    <li>template engine - <a target="_blank" href="https://ejs.co/">ejs</a></li>
    <li>DI tool - <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/typestack/typedi">typedi</a></li>
</ul>

